## Tested before trusted

A typecheck-passing build is not a verified build.
A "looks good by inspection" review is not a tested change.
A green CI is not a working feature.

Verify by RUNNING the code in conditions that match production:
- Same data shapes
- Same integrations live
- Same user roles you'll have in prod

For multi-user features (calendar, sharing, permissions): test as TWO
users in TWO browser sessions before declaring done.

