## On Claude Code and Cursor

These tools are powerful but they don't enforce discipline. We do.

- A typecheck-passing prompt result is not a verified change.
- A "looks good by inspection" review is not a tested change.
- A multi-section prompt is multiple changes, even if it's one PR.

Treat AI-assisted code with the same scrutiny as junior-developer code.
Sometimes more, because AI is confident even when wrong.

For when to use which tool, see `10_tooling_guide.md`.

